summary: Aftab Store - Internet Identity integration project with custom domain configuration
architectural_notes: Internet Identity integration with alternative origins for custom domains (v2.aftabstore.com, aftabstore.com)
ii-alternative-origins file in .well-known directory for domain compatibility

existing_features.title: Overwrite the content of frontend/public/.well-known/ii-alternative-origins with the following exact JSON: {"alternativeOrigins": ["https://v2.aftabstore.com","https://www.v2.aftabstore.com","https://aftabstore.com","https://www.aftabstore.com"]}
